{"text": "Real talk: The original mod of The Haunted kept Unreal Tournament 3 installed on my hard drive long after I gave up on the single-player campaign of the original game, because I could always come back to The Haunted for a quick shoot-em-up session. With the full version, not a lot has really changed for the better: What started as a fun little knock-off of Resident Evil's Mercenaries mode is now a kind of boring and listless arcade shooter that plays stiffly and doesn't meaningfully iterate or reinvent on either the original or its inspiration. If you're curious, just download the original mod instead. You'll thank me later.", "appid": "43190", "steamid": "profiles/76561197980724275", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0}
